    <p class="mb-4">
      Finland has excellent public healthcare through municipal health centers and hospitals. As a registered entrepreneur paying social contributions, you access Kela benefits including healthcare subsidies.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Healthcare Options</h3>

